Revision history for Perl extension Apache::SimpleReplace.

0.01  4.4.2000
	- original version
        - actually a rename of (the now obsolete) Apache::Wrapper_0.02

0.02  05.08.2000
	- fixed embarassing parsing of Filter PerlSetVar (whoops)
	- TEMPLATE is no longer relative to server root
        - minor pod changes

0.03  05.15.2000
        - corrected installation to install to a versioned
          directory (whoops)

0.04  05.25.2000
        - fixed bug in status checking when not using Apache::Filter
        - return SERVER_ERROR if Apache::Filter or Apache::File
          can't open the file
